init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's a theater with rows of seats going up, and you're on the bottom floor.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You continue to watch the film, and you see yourself in a beautiful scene.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You have the memory of that joy hundreds of times.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Then you see something in the film that makes you incredibly sad.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You now know that you have been a neglectful parent hundreds of times.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The other people in the audience who are you, give you a knowing look.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You're not alone, there are hundreds of you.
